---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '03.05.2026';
---
<BaseLayout
  locale="en"
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy regarding the processing of personal data on this website."
>
  <main class="page" id="main-content">
    <section class="page-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">Legal Information</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="muted">
        This privacy policy explains the type, scope, and purpose of personal data processing on
        this website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card legal-card">
      <h2>1. Controller</h2>
      <address>
        Patrick Scharf<br />
        Am Liedlein 3b<br />
        97222 Rimpar<br />
        Germany
      </address>
      <p>E-Mail: <a href="mailto:Softwareentwickler@tutamail.com">Softwareentwickler@tutamail.com</a></p>
    </section>

    <section class="card legal-card">
      <h2>2. Access Data and Hosting</h2>
      <p>
        When this website is accessed, the hosting provider processes technically required
        information (for example IP address, date/time, requested resource, browser type) to ensure
        secure and stable operation.
      </p>
      <p>Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interest in secure operation).</p>
      <p>Hosting provider: Cloudflare</p>
    </section>

    <section class="card legal-card">
      <h2>3. Contact Requests</h2>
      <p>
        If you contact us by e-mail, your provided information will be stored for processing your
        request and potential follow-up questions.
      </p>
      <p>Legal basis: Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR (pre-contractual communication).</p>
    </section>

    <section class="card legal-card">
      <h2>4. Recipients and Transfer</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data is only disclosed where necessary for contract fulfilment, where legally
        required, or where explicit consent has been granted.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card legal-card">
      <h2>5. Storage Period</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data is stored only as long as required for the respective purposes or where legal
        retention obligations apply.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="card legal-card">
      <h2>6. Data Subject Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Under applicable law, you have rights of access, rectification, erasure, restriction of
        processing, data portability, and objection to the processing of personal data.
      </p>
      <p>
        You also have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority, in particular in
        the EU member state of your habitual residence, your place of work, or the place of the
        alleged infringement.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="muted legal-meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
